channel.description:
What this basically does is restock all the shops to the Amount set on the shops configuration file
Example 
Out of stock Fire Rune 
After command reload shops
In stock fire rune

Add this Command
[code]	if(command.equalsIgnoreCase("reloadshops") && playerRights > 2)
	{
	server.shopHandler.reloadshops();
		sM("Shops Reloaded");
	}[/code]

Then Add this method into ShopHandler Class
[code]	public void reloadshops()
	{
			for (int i = 0; i < MaxShops; i++) {
			for (int j = 0; j < MaxShopItems; j++) {
				ResetItem(i, j);
				ShopItemsSN[i][j] = 0; // Special resetting, only at begin !
			}
			ShopItemsStandard[i] = 0; // Special resetting, only at begin !
			ShopSModifier[i] = 0;
			ShopBModifier[i] = 0;
			ShopName[i] = "";
		}
		TotalShops = 0;
		loadShops("shops.cfg");
		}[/code]
